-- Indian Oil Corp. Approves Selling 242.8 Million Shares
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-09-21T03:08:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/indian-oil-corp-approves-selling-242-8-million-shares.html

          
          
             Indian Oil Corp. approved selling
as many as 242.8 million shares, or 10 percent of its equity,
through a public offer along with a government share sale,
according to a statement today on the Bombay Stock Exchange.  
          
          


  


        